{"tid":1537440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「跳閘有意義」我明白點解咁少人跳閘","createTime":"2019-09-04T02:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:58:51.000Z","uid":36716,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"70851ed7997259b30684513e15187e87726e0bf3","tid":1537440,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"有唔跳閘但發過夢既人原因係<br />\n<br />\n非法集會錯不在自己，係政府<br />\n但跳閘就係錯在自己<br />\n<br />\n我理解佢地會覺得過唔到道德標準<br />\n<br />\n但如果<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>每跳一次就捐10蚊比星火同盟<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n會唔會令大家覺得有意義呢<br />\n<br />\n明白個數唔多，但一人一小步就可以好多"},{"pid":"e68667d635b09ae7714d35e7c377581c8647bde1","tid":1537440,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:27:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b749729777a80e45e86f80c7349ee6415f36160","tid":1537440,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6975b711735ae7b3df8e31277204b85e398e784","tid":1537440,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，長久戰、拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪、減少淘寶<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點咆哮！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n5. 不要說推，試著將呢段訊息copy and paste嚟推post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 每星期做孝子，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少碰中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.04"},{"pid":"06ad32ed73c49d3d9c54bd313366ffe6f4e20e24","tid":1537440,"uid":111982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:28:52.000Z","msg":"【Google 廣告】上線啦 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535377</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請多多關注 比下意見"},{"pid":"89af63b95bb39b336ec7c4ed59bfc88d332ddb59","tid":1537440,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"